<i>♪ I can hear the whole world
Say it's now or never ♪</i>

298
00:50:07,212 --> 00:50:11,508
<i>♪ 'Cause it's not too late
If we change our ways ♪</i>

299
00:50:11,591 --> 00:50:15,053
<i>♪ And connect the dots to our problems ♪</i>

300
